# TESTING ENHANCEMENT GUIDELINES

## Test Structure
- Use `test.each` for parameterized tests with multiple scenarios
- Write unit tests FIRST, integration tests SECOND
- We want to validate any number of scenarios, with unit testing and keep integration tests for validating clear scenarios.
- Cover edge cases and error conditions
- Use factory functions for test object creation

## Test Data Management
- Create realistic test data that mirrors production
- Use factory functions for test object creation
- Clean up test data after each test
- Test with different user roles and permissions